layerGroup.title: Regions of Common Profile (RCP) - Kerguelen Plateau: Hard classification
layerGroup.abstractTxt: A layer group combining the "hard classification" of Regions of Common Profile (RCP) for the Kerguelen Plateau, together with ancillary information available in map popups: for each classified RCP, (1) biological and environmental characteristics; and (2) a full species list (and probability of occurrence).
